<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101080727678214></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101080727678214><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=4431&mid=101080727678214>Haste...</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=4431&mid=101080727678214#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a>, <span id=Guru>Guru</span><br><span id=notbold>559 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jan 11th 10:47 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK here's the story guys:<br><br>Haste increases the number of swings in a unit of time.&nbsp;&nbsp;So, this 20% haste adds 20% to the number of swings you get in x amount of time.  If weapon delay is 20 (delay is tenths of a second), you get one swing every 2 seconds or 30 swings a minute.  Add 20% --&gt; 36 swings a minute.  New delay = (60/36)*10 = 16.7 (may round to 17)<br><br>This is a spell/song haste.  You can have exactly ONE spell/song haste, with two specific exceptions.  There are 2 bard songs that give 5% and 10% haste that stack with spell haste.  All other songs do NOT stack - both icons appear, you get all other bonuses from both hastes but only the higher haste takes effect.<br><br>Spell/song haste stacks with item haste.  So, if you're wearing FBSS and this, your haste is 20% + 21% (FBSS) = 41%.<br><br>Your new weapon delay = Old Delay / (1+ 0.41)<br><br>re Haste caps.  Best info I've seen is that Haste caps at 85% up to level 50 or 51, and 100% after that.  So, best you can do is reduce delay by half. 1/(1 + 1.00) = 0.5<br><br>re minimum delays - There is a minimum, supposedly, but it is based on the weapon and is NOT 10.  Monks have shown that you can get delay down below 10.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
