	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Sep 17th 10:25 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>so ....<br><br>Haste DOES affect how much *damage* you do over time! If you do x damage every y seconds, then in z seconds you do x(z/y) damage. As you can see from basic algebra, if you decrease y (i.e. hit more often) then you increase the damage.<br><br>Q.E.D.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
